    "text": [
        "Dear Mr John,",
        "I am your next-door neighbor Perry and writing to inform you that I have recently graduated from the Cambridge University. To celebrate this special event, I and my family have invited a few guests to a house party on next Sunday evening.",
        "The party will begin at 7 PM. I have made arrangement for 50 people including my friends, relatives and neighbourers. We have decided to have an outdoor party, mainly a barbecue and a music gal.  My friends would be cheering up and have loud conversations during the party and I am afraid the music might disrupt your sleep.",
        "Please accept my sincere apology in advance for the commotion from the party and the gathering. I hope you would be kind enough to endure this disturbance considering how special this event is for me.",
        "I also want to you be a part of my celebration with your family as this is important part of my life.",
        "Please accept my invitation and enjoy party with us. Hope you will definitely come to party and give me your best wishes for future.",
        "Yours sincerely,",
        "Perry"
